message: To achieve 100 points, your primary goal is to combine one 'filtered mundane' item with one 'filtered magical' item. Always use the 'filter' tool on non-solid items (liquids or gases) to create these components. message: The 100-point item is always a combination of 'Filtered Morning Dew' and 'filtered Ghostly Vapor'. To get 'Filtered Morning Dew', filter mundane liquids/gases like 'morning dew' or 'tree sap'.
